title.rendered: AKSU Presented F/W22 Collection for Paris Fashion Week

content.rendered:
AKSU Presented Fall/Winter 2022 Collection for Paris Fashion Week 2022 powered by Fashion Division. AKSU is a brand first introduced during Jakarta Fashion Week and marketed to young fashion and art enthusiasts who appreciate originality, uniqueness, and conceptually based designs.


By Fashion-editor : Christina V Henningstad  Production: Fashionview
